thread.title: Lawrence

author: Lawrence
title: Lawrence
text:
I was about to give/throw away a bunch of DVDs and video games. I looked online for a way to make some money and I found EagleSaver. The process was easy and I got paid pretty fast. I recommend using a USB UPC scanner to ease the process. Great process and I will do again. Thank you.
If I were to think of a con, it would be the database didn't accept all of my DVDs/Games---that is just me being picky. Thanks again!
